{"tid":1185994,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"係telegram谷中見到香港仲有得救","createTime":"2019-06-04T15:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T04:45:43.000Z","uid":205098,"like":49,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"853de9675681c14e3cdb45f355d53da4c2043ada","tid":1185994,"uid":205098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T15:16:12.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟我係連登無意中見到個group叫六月九日撐逃犯條例遊行工作群。<br />\n<br />\n咁我原本諗住入去屌下班人，結果入到去發覺好似有啲奇怪，望真啲「6月9號 2點半 維園草地集合」，仆你個街，原黎係假膠group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z5SESqQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ5SESqQ.png&h=07c4d728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見到有機會撚鳩班為咗錢寧願出賣香港嘅廢青/中/老，梗係要參與埋一份玩下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後尾我哋就作咗下面呢段嘢出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">6.9支持逃犯條例遊行\n\n日期：6月9日（日）\n集合地點：維園草地\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步\n\n\n支持逃犯條例白宮聯署\n-簽完記得確認返電郵\n\nhttps://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\n\n各位愛國同胞一定要簽 俾班黃屍睇下有幾多人支持逃犯條例\n\n為獎勵愛國表現，黨將贈予\n進入連結並成功簽署：500元人民幣\n完成6．9 當天遊行：1000元人民幣\n(準備支付寶/微信 , 遊行完結後於tg聯絡)</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n結果又真係撚到啲人幫手簽名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VishD9k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVishD9k.png&h=5f0da59c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vk1BUHO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVk1BUHO.png&h=d5b2bf07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過其實撚到人都唔係最緊要，最緊要係見到<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有更多嘅人入黎呢個谷 目的係為咗屌鳩我哋</strong></span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yGfveT2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyGfveT2.png&h=a284bd26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ucdwJD0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FucdwJD0.png&h=86b05166&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fs843D5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffs843D5.png&h=1c03265e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好開心見到大多數香港人都仲係清醒嘅，明白咩係是非黑白，無乜人會真係為咗500蚊港紙出賣良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即使知道個group全部人都奶緊共，都會嘗試入黎同我哋理論/屌醒我哋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以大家千祈唔好話香港已死，香港係仲有一大班面對公義會發聲嘅人，香港係仲有得救㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以6月9號唔好再返工不了，大家到時見。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2891604d9037eca5dad72f4e47bccffd14497e70","tid":1185994,"uid":205098,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T15:18:02.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b7dcefdb9c8faebf2644a876ec0a2b4733a085","tid":1185994,"uid":205098,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T15:19:37.000Z","msg":"而呢為扮撐中巴打嘅icon ⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rEHhEdi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrEHhEdi.png&h=e940f839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TwjPvj2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTwjPvj2.png&h=9e2a7134&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc6ad3ef6c6c20f37443e3464ace99b252496666","tid":1185994,"uid":205098,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201